== Etymology ==

Coined in 1972 by Stanley Cohen, who coined the phrase to describe media coverage of Mobs and Rockers in Great Britain in the 1960s.

== Meaning ==

A semi-spontaneous or media-generated mass movement based on the perception that an individual, group, or community is dangerously deviant and poses a menace to society.

